<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Complete Submission Guide - ACO Service</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --brand-400: #60a5fa;
            --brand-500: #a78bfa;
            --bg: #f5f7fb;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --text-900: #0f172a;
            --text-700: #334155;
            --text-600: #475569;
            --muted: #94a3b8;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --info: #3b82f6;
            --radius-lg: 12px;
            --shadow-md: 0 10px 25px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }
        [data-theme="dark"] {
            --bg: #000000;
            --surface: #111827;
            --text-900: #e5e7eb;
            --text-700: #cbd5e1;
            --text-600: #94a3b8;
            --muted: #64748b;
            --border: #1f2937;
        }
        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-700);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .guide-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            background-color: var(--surface);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .guide-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-500), var(--brand-400));
            color: white;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .guide-header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .guide-header p {
            margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .guide-content {
            padding: 2.5rem;
        }
        .guide-section {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        .guide-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-900);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .guide-section h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-900);
            margin-top: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .field-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .field-list li {
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .field-list li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .field-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-900);
        }
        .field-desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            text-align: right;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--info);
            padding: 1.25rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: var(--text-700);
        }
        .code-block {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .code-block code {
            font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-700);
        }
        .copy-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-500), var(--brand-400));
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }
        .copy-btn:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .fake-menu {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-700);
        }
        ol {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        ol li {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="guide-container">
        <div class="guide-header">
            <h1>Complete Submission Guide</h1>
            <p>Your step-by-step guide to filling out your information securely.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-content">

            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>General Information (Pre-filled)</h2>
                <p>When you open the form, some fields will be automatically filled for you. You don't need to change these.</p>
                <ul class="field-list">
                    <li><span class="field-name">Discord ID:</span> <span class="field-desc">Your unique Discord user ID.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Discord Username:</span> <span class="field-desc">Your Discord username (e.g., "user#1234").</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Service Name:</span> <span class="field-desc">The name of the service you're subscribing to.</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>No Login Services</h2>
                <p>This section applies to services that don't require us to log into a retail account on your behalf (e.g., Shopify, Pokemon Center).</p>
                
                <h3>Shipping Information</h3>
                <p>Please enter your full and correct shipping address.</p>
                <ul class="field-list">
                    <li><span class="field-name">Shipping Address - Street:</span> <span class="field-desc">Your street address (e.g., "123 Main St").</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Shipping Address - City:</span> <span class="field-desc">The city you live in.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Shipping Address - State:</span> <span class="field-desc">Your state or province (e.g., "CA").</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Shipping Address - ZIP Code:</span> <span class="field-desc">Your postal or ZIP code.</span></li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Payment Information</h3>
                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>Security Note:</strong> Your payment information is encrypted with AES-256 and only used for processing your checkouts.
                </div>
                <ul class="field-list">
                    <li><span class="field-name">Payment - Card Number:</span> <span class="field-desc">Your 16-digit credit or debit card number.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Payment - Expiration (MM/YY):</span> <span class="field-desc">Card expiry date in MM/YY format.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Payment - CVV:</span> <span class="field-desc">The 3 or 4-digit security code from your card.</span></li>
                    <li><span class="field-name">Payment - Billing ZIP:</span> <span class="field-desc">The ZIP code associated with your card.</span></li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Contact Information</h3>
                <ul class="field-list">
                    <li><span class="field-name">Phone Number:</span> <span class="field-desc">Used for order notifications.</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="guide-section">
                <h2>Login Required Services</h2>
                <p>This applies to services where we need to log into a retail account for you (e.g., Target, Best Buy). It includes all fields from "No Login Services" plus the following:</p>

                <h3>Gmail App Password for IMAP</h3>
                <div class="info-box">
                    To find a Gmail app password for IMAP, go to your Google Account's "App passwords" page at <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords" target="_blank">myaccount.google.com/apppasswords</a>.
                    Enable 2-Step Verification if you haven't already. Then, click "Generate". Select the app and device you're using, and a 16-digit password will be created for you to use in your email client's IMAP settings instead of your regular password.
                </div>
                <p>Please enter this 16-digit app password in the "IMAP App Password" field when submitting your information.</p>
                <ul class="field-list">
                    <li><span class="field-name">IMAP App Password:</span> <span class="field-desc">The 16-digit app password generated from your Google Account.</span></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function copyToClipboard(text) {
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
                const button = event.target;
                const originalText = button.textContent;
                button.textContent = 'Copied!';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    button.textContent = originalText;
                }, 2000);
            }, (err) => {
                alert('Failed to copy: ', err);
            });
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>